profile.xml: <?xml version="1.0" encoding="UTF-8"?><profile version="6000000">    <face_characteristics>		<!-- Ensure decent pose -->        <pose_angle_yaw min="-20" pref="0" max="20" qWeight="1.0" />		<pose_angle_pitch min="-15" pref="0" max="15" qWeight="1.0"/>		<!-- Disallow faces that are egregiously lit -->        <facial_dynamic_range min="7.0" max="8.0" />    </face_characteristics>    <eye_characteristics>		<!-- Eyes must be open -->        <left_eye_closed_likelihood min="0" pref="0" max="75" qWeight="5.0" />        <right_eye_closed_likelihood min="0" pref="0" max="75" qWeight="5.0" />    </eye_characteristics>    <image_characteristics>		<!-- Extended Pixel Padding Type -->        <background_pad_type min="2" pref="2" max="2" />    </image_characteristics>    <anomalies>		<!-- Do not allow Dark Glasses -->        <dark_glasses_likelihood min="0" pref="0" max="50" />    </anomalies>    <image_geometry>        <image_width pref="480" />		<image_height pref="640" />		<!-- Higher Eye Separation requires the user be closer to the Camera. -->        <eye_separation min="70" />		<!-- Pose Roll -->		<eye_axis_angle min="-5" pref="0" max="5" />		<!-- Position of the face in image -->        <eye_axis_location_ratio min="0.45" pref="0.55" max="0.65" />        <centerline_location_ratio min="0.42" pref="0.5" max="0.58" />		<!-- Head Width is a Maximum of 74% of the Image's Width -->        <image_width_to_head_width_ratio min="1.35" pref="1.5" max="1.7" />		<!-- Head Height is Maximum of 60% of the Image's Height -->        <head_height_to_image_height_ratio min="0.4" pref="0.53" max="0.8" />    </image_geometry>    <image_storage>		<!-- Image Format 4 is JPEG -->        <image_format min="4" pref="4" max="4" />		<jpeg_quality_level min="80" pref="100" max="100" />    </image_storage></profile>
